804
00:35:42,083 --> 00:35:44,041
Yeah, I have some stuff
I can take care of here, too,

805
00:35:44,083 --> 00:35:47,083
but, um...

806
00:35:47,125 --> 00:35:51,041
I can, uh, I can
meet at your place.

807
00:35:51,083 --> 00:35:54,125
