852
00:38:13,583 --> 00:38:14,750
Hey.

853
00:38:14,792 --> 00:38:16,458
♪ Still nothing's heard ♪

854
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:18,125
What time is it?

855
00:38:18,166 --> 00:38:23,000
Uh, it's...
It's about 9:00.

856
00:38:23,041 --> 00:38:25,041
♪ So if someone
can see me now ♪

857
00:38:25,083 --> 00:38:28,250
♪ let them see you ♪

858
00:38:28,291 --> 00:38:30,041
You know,
I've been here all day,

859
00:38:30,083 --> 00:38:32,875
just in case
you were wondering.

860
00:38:32,917 --> 00:38:34,542
Worrying about me?

861
00:38:34,583 --> 00:38:36,041
Well, you're my best friend,

862
00:38:36,083 --> 00:38:38,792
which is sad,
because you're 8 years old

863
00:38:38,834 --> 00:38:42,041
and... you don't return
my affections,

864
00:38:42,083 --> 00:38:45,291
but ah, well, there it is.

865
00:38:45,333 --> 00:38:47,875
You're my best friend.

866
00:38:51,250 --> 00:38:53,625
It's okay to laugh.

867
00:38:53,667 --> 00:38:56,625
It happens.

868
00:38:56,667 --> 00:38:59,834
♪ So if someone
could help me now ♪

869
00:38:59,875 --> 00:39:02,041
I had a baby, Sheldon.

870
00:39:02,083 --> 00:39:04,041
♪ Mm ♪

871
00:39:04,083 --> 00:39:07,542
For a few minutes there...

872
00:39:07,583 --> 00:39:09,834
I was someone's mom.

873
00:39:09,875 --> 00:39:11,208
♪ See you through ♪

874
00:39:11,250 --> 00:39:13,125
You're still someone's mom.

875
00:39:13,166 --> 00:39:15,417
He's just not--
not here anymore.

876
00:39:15,458 --> 00:39:19,166
♪ We've all gotta do ♪

877
00:39:19,208 --> 00:39:21,041
I missed you.

878
00:39:21,083 --> 00:39:22,333
♪ Ooh ♪

879
00:39:22,375 --> 00:39:26,041
♪ and so you wouldn't
be wrong ♪

880
00:39:26,083 --> 00:39:27,834
♪ bein' free, you and me ♪

881
00:39:27,875 --> 00:39:30,041
It's okay to cry.

882
00:39:30,083 --> 00:39:31,625
It happens.

883
00:39:34,792 --> 00:39:38,417
♪ Mm-mm ♪

884
00:39:38,458 --> 00:39:41,667
