00:39:55,542 --> 00:39:58,458
Like, for a long time?

892
00:39:58,500 --> 00:40:00,458
♪ Mm-mm, mm-mm ♪

893
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:03,291
♪ mm-mm ♪

894
00:40:03,333 --> 00:40:05,417
What if I blew it, Violet?

895
00:40:05,458 --> 00:40:07,208
♪ Mm-mm ♪

