I-I should've said yes,

917
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:47,291
so i'm--I'm saying yes now.

918
00:40:47,333 --> 00:40:49,041
Well, it's too late.
I love you.

919
00:40:49,083 --> 00:40:50,542
You know, I just told you,
it's too late.

920
00:40:50,583 --> 00:40:52,625
I'm in love with you.
