927
00:41:00,083 --> 00:41:01,208
Look, you were right.

928
00:41:01,250 --> 00:41:02,959
I... I didn't want a baby.

929
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:06,291
And I don't.
I don't want a baby.

930
00:41:06,333 --> 00:41:08,875
I want this baby.

931
00:41:08,917 --> 00:41:10,041
I want Henry.

932
00:41:10,083 --> 00:41:11,750
And... I want you

933
00:41:11,792 --> 00:41:14,166
